title: Days of internet past: Tech Weekly presents Updog – podcast
text:
Days of internet past: Tech Weekly presents Updog – podcast Elena and Alex get misty eyed about the days of ye olde internete when the world wide web was black and white and needed winding up in the morning Subscribe via iTunes Download MP3 Podcast feed URL Presented by Elena Cresci and Alex Hern , produced by Alannah Chance
Friday 25 September 2015 09.05 BST
Share on Facebook Share on Twitter Share via Email Share on Pinterest Share on LinkedIn Share on Google+ Share on WhatsApp In this week's instalment of Updog – our podcast dedicated to internet memes and all things digitally viral – Alex Hern and Elena Cresci trawl through the dusty corners of the internet to look back at the days of dial-up modems, LiveJournal and neopets.
Elena's finally admits to her career plan B, Ginny Weasley Fanfic.
